**Lab vs natural verdict:** Lab for maximum size at any budget; natural in the JA Bezel Platinum series for investment/heirloom
**Top picks:** Lab 1 ct YG $930 (best value); Lab 3 ct YG $2,292 (best impact); JA Bezel Natural 0.25 ct YG $892 (daily-wear natural); JA Bezel Natural 1 ct Platinum $5,859 (heirloom); EW Bezel 0.25 CTW WG $1,220 (modern/layering)
